{"tid":1643138,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【蘋果跪低】「HKmap.live即時地圖」遭下架","createTime":"2019-10-10T03:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T03:56:54.000Z","uid":37112,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d32f7e073894188d95673db871107cdde5fd5e5","tid":1643138,"uid":37112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"【蘋果跪低】蘋果將追蹤警方行蹤APP「HKmap.live即時地圖」下架 (11:27)<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2019年10月10日<br />\n<br />\n本港示威行動持續，早前遭內地官媒點名批評、可以實時顯示警員及警車身處位置等的手機應用程式「HKmap.live即時地圖」，據報已被蘋果公司(Apple)從應用商店中下架。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》引用App Store聲明報道，指「HKmap.live即時地圖」被香港示威者用來追踪警察的行動，相關應用程式會危及執法。聲明提到，香港網絡安全及科技罪案調查科指出，由於該應用程式顯示警察的位置，有理由相信該應用程序已被用於瞄準（target）和伏擊（ambush）香港警察。<br />\n<br />\n「HKmap.live即時地圖」，可實時顯示警員及警車身處位置、何處施放了催淚彈等。此前，「HKmap.live即時地圖」曾遭蘋果以會鼓勵進行違法活動為由拒絕上架申請，開發者其後上訴，Apple最終批准。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20191010/s00002/1570679401675/%e3%80%90%e8%98%8b%e6%9e%9c%e8%b7%aa%e4%bd%8e%e3%80%91%e8%98%8b%e6%9e%9c%e5%b0%87%e8%bf%bd%e8%b9%a4%e8%ad%a6%e6%96%b9%e8%a1%8c%e8%b9%a4app%e3%80%8chkmap-live%e5%8d%b3%e6%99%82%e5%9c%b0%e5%9c%96%e3%80%8d%e4%b8%8b%e6%9e%b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20191010%2Fs00002%2F1570679401675%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%2598%258b%25e6%259e%259c%25e8%25b7%25aa%25e4%25bd%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e8%2598%258b%25e6%259e%259c%25e5%25b0%2587%25e8%25bf%25bd%25e8%25b9%25a4%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%2596%25b9%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%25b9%25a4app%25e3%2580%258chkmap-live%25e5%258d%25b3%25e6%2599%2582%25e5%259c%25b0%25e5%259c%2596%25e3%2580%258d%25e4%25b8%258b%25e6%259e%25b6&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2EmxdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=59d99894\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e7%25b6%2593%25e6%25bf%259f%2Farticle%2F20191010%2Fs00002%2F1570679401675%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%2598%258b%25e6%259e%259c%25e8%25b7%25aa%25e4%25bd%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e